--- !u!114 &465533053
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 465533051}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 48fdfcc8a67199e4aa51c8e7b7b14715, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::WitcherRightVersion.Dialogue.DialogueInteractable
  displayName: Marta Lozovaya
  interactionPrompt: Talk
  startNodeId: start
  returnToElderNodeId: 
  completedQuestNodeId: 
  dialogueNodes:
  - Id: start
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: You walk like someone hired by Voytsekh. If he sent you south, do not trust
      dry boots and clean stories.
    Choices:
    - Text: I took the swamp contract. What do you know?
      NextNodeId: swamp_poison
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why does the village fear the swamp?
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I need herbs and remedies.
      NextNodeId: antitoxin
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Later.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: swamp_poison
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: The mud itself bites now. Look for black slime on the road, torn reeds,
      and tracks that sink too deep. If you smell rot before you see water, draw
      silver.
    Choices:
    - Text: Then I start with the tracks.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
    - Text: Tell me about antidotes.
      NextNodeId: antitoxin
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Why is this happening?
      NextNodeId: curse
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
  - Id: curse
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: A normal swamp kills slowly. This one remembers. People call Elsa a witch
      because it is easier than asking what the village buried.
    Choices:
    - Text: That sounds bigger than a monster.
      NextNodeId: warning
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Back to the contract.
      NextNodeId: swamp_poison
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: Enough for now.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: warning
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: It is. But first survive the thing in the reeds. Truth is useless if you
      drown before reaching it.
    Choices:
    - Text: Show me how to stay alive.
      NextNodeId: antitoxin
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 0
    - Text: I will inspect the tracks.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
  - Id: antitoxin
    SpeakerName: Marta Lozovaya
    Body: Boil bogweed with a little monster slime and keep it bitter. Proper antitoxin
      comes later, once you bring proof from the swamp.
    Choices:
    - Text: I will remember that.
      NextNodeId: 
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: 
      ClosesDialogue: 1
    - Text: Tell me about the tracks.
      NextNodeId: swamp_poison
      FlagToSet: 
      QuestAction: marta_spoken
      ClosesDialogue: 0
